Oh, no?

215
00:27:04,150 --> 00:27:05,460
因为我们在这里
'Cause here we are.

216
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:09,190
浪费了一天追踪敌人的时间  只因为你
Losing a day of tracking our enemy 'cause you --

217
