I just see a guy who wants to get in your pants.

227
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,560
好吧
Fine.

228
00:28:13,360 --> 00:28:14,170
好吧
Fine.

229
00:28:15,310 --> 00:28:18,440
他是忍不住盯着他所爱过的人
Who couldn't stop gazing at somebody he loved.

230
00:28:20,740 --> 00:28:22,790
我没说过他爱过我
I never said he loved me.

231
00:28:25,630 --> 00:28:28,850
你今天本可以在外面杀了他
You could've ended him out there today,

232
00:28:29,420 --> 00:28:30,590
而你没下手
and you didn't.

233
00:28:32,450 --> 00:28:33,340
为什么
Why?

234
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:37,890
