At one point, he meant something to me, yeah.

235
00:28:39,330 --> 00:28:40,990
我对此没有隐瞒
I've been open about that.

236
00:28:43,890 --> 00:28:46,670
但在你找到了我  我选择了这个大家庭的那天
But it ended the day you found me

237
00:28:46,670 --> 00:28:48,170
