and I chose this family,

238
00:28:48,170 --> 00:28:51,220
我从没有后悔过做出那个决定
and I have never once regretted that decision,

239
00:28:51,220 --> 00:28:53,360
我也不希望你后悔
and I don't want you to, either.

240
00:28:54,530 --> 00:28:55,370
你后悔吗
Do you?

241
00:29:09,050 --> 00:29:10,470
