I believe in you.

242
00:29:14,280 --> 00:29:16,460
相比其他人来说
More than the others.

243
00:29:19,020 --> 00:29:20,090
我知道
I know.

244
00:29:22,990 --> 00:29:24,600
你觉得我们可以信任他吗
You think we can trust him?

245
00:29:26,450 --> 00:29:27,160
可以
Yeah.

246
00:29:31,260 --> 00:29:31,990
好
Good.

247
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:35,690
让我亲眼看看
Now, let me see for myself.

248
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,270
