Aww, Shaw ain't nobody's girlfriend.

253
00:29:52,010 --> 00:29:54,950
我敢打赌这小子什么都听她的
I'm betting she wears the pants with homeboy here.

254
00:29:55,100 --> 00:29:56,160
你说是不是
Isn't that right?

255
00:29:56,580 --> 00:29:59,070
你屁都不懂  卡弗  闭嘴吧
You don't know shit about shit, Carver. Knock it off.

256
00:30:01,970 --> 00:30:04,210
那我还是出去吧
I guess I'll just show my dumb ass out, then.

257
00:30:15,830 --> 00:30:16,910
教皇快来了
Pope is on his way.

258
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:19,680
在我见他之前  你想提醒我什么吗
Anything you wanna tell me about this guy before I meet him?

259
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:21,470
看我眼色行事
Just follow my lead.

260
00:30:57,690 --> 00:30:59,520
给  拿着
Here! Take it! Take it!

261
00:31:13,270 --> 00:31:15,260
用这个
Here! Here!

262
00:31:43,120 --> 00:31:44,460
快
Come on.

263
00:32:43,990 --> 00:32:46,110
由火铸就
Forged by fire.

264
00:32:47,790 --> 00:32:50,980
由神指定
Ordained by God.

265
00:32:52,760 --> 00:32:53,950
欢迎他
Welcome him!

266
00:32:54,690 --> 00:32:56,690
出自《圣经》拉丁语版钦定本诗篇140:8
指上帝在争战之中赐予我勇气
赴汤蹈火
Fortitudo Saludis!

267
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:06,070
你信上帝吗
You believe in God?

268
00:33:08,780 --> 00:33:10,910
不信
No. No, I don't.

269
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:13,440
不再信了
Not anymore.

270
00:33:14,490 --> 00:33:16,320
我现在只信自己
Guess I just believe in me now.

271
00:33:17,540 --> 00:33:18,980
这是个错误
Well, that's a mistake.

272
00:33:20,090 --> 00:33:22,060
-为何  -因为你不是上帝
- Why's that? - 'Cause you're not Him.

273
00:33:23,910 --> 00:33:25,610
我通过了你的小测试
I passed your little test, didn't I?

274
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:27,480
无论你怎么称呼那事
Whatever you want to call it.

275
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:29,610
你以为这就结束了吗
Oh, and you think that's the end of it?

276
00:33:31,210 --> 00:33:32,700
你还想要我做什么
What else do you want from me?

277
00:33:34,150 --> 00:33:35,170
我想要
I want...

278
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:40,220
我想要你理解
I want you to understand.

279
00:33:50,990 --> 00:33:51,800
坐
Sit down.

280
00:33:56,950 --> 00:34:01,330
我们都是在死亡谷认识的
We all met in the Valley of Death.

281
00:34:02,270 --> 00:34:04,370
反正我们是这样称呼那里的
That's what we call it, anyway.

282
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:07,290
阿富汗的山区
Hills of Afghanistan.

283
00:34:07,710 --> 00:34:09,280
我们为国奋战
We fought for our country,

284
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:12,240
把阵亡的战友抬下战场
carried our fallen brothers off the field.

285
00:34:12,860 --> 00:34:15,660
抬了太多人  后来我们都数不清了
Carried so many, we lost count after a while.

286
00:34:19,890 --> 00:34:21,320
政客们
Politicians.

287
00:34:24,860 --> 00:34:26,390
只管开支票
They wrote the checks.

288
00:34:26,930 --> 00:34:28,560
根本不在乎我们
We weren't anything to them.

289
00:34:28,830 --> 00:34:30,020
我们只是道具
Just props.

290
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,960
下次竞选所用的道具
Props for their next campaign.

291
00:34:33,290 --> 00:34:36,490
他们喜欢谈论上帝
See, they -- they talked about God.

292
00:34:38,390 --> 00:34:39,870
他们不认识上帝
They didn't know God.

293
00:34:40,610 --> 00:34:42,280
他们没见过他的脸
They never saw His face.

294
00:34:43,650 --> 00:34:45,060
不像我们
It's not like we did.

295
00:34:45,690 --> 00:34:48,650
我们看到上帝无处不在
We saw God everywhere.

296
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:53,210
他在鲜血  恐怖和死亡之中
He was in the blood and the horror and death.

297
00:34:53,890 --> 00:34:57,860
他在那  为我们指引方向
He was there, telling us where to go.

298
00:35:00,730 --> 00:35:04,800
在那段日子里  我们唯有指望他
Didn't have much else to hold on to in those days but Him.

299
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:07,920
还有彼此
And each other.

300
00:35:11,420 --> 00:35:12,270
你抽烟吗
You smoke?

301
00:35:27,810 --> 00:35:32,970
那场战争差点永远废了我们
That war damn near ruined all of us for good.

302
00:35:33,070 --> 00:35:36,900
回国之后  我的部下都有永久性损伤
Came home and my guys had permanent injuries.

303
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:40,450
他们睡不着觉  找不到正经工作
They couldn't sleep. They couldn't find real jobs.

304
00:35:42,600 --> 00:35:43,520
所以
So...

305
00:35:46,120 --> 00:35:48,270
我们成了人们口中的佣兵
people called us mercenaries.

306
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:52,620
那些没人想做的脏活累活
We did all the ugly, dirty work

307
00:35:52,620 --> 00:35:54,590
都由我们来做
nobody else wanted to do.

308
00:35:55,790 --> 00:35:58,480
还拿到了丰厚的佣金
Got paid for it, too. Handsomely.

309
00:36:03,810 --> 00:36:06,860
真正的脏活是在沦陷之后开始的
The real dirty work started after the Fall.

310
00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:15,230
我从没有经历过那样的战争
Never been in a war like that.

311
00:36:18,470 --> 00:36:21,610
从没有见过那样的混乱
Never seen that kind of chaos,

312
00:36:22,030 --> 00:36:24,990
而我以前什么都见过
and I had seen everything.

313
00:36:27,640 --> 00:36:28,620
但这个
But this...

314
00:36:33,150 --> 00:36:35,170
我们做的那些事
Oh, the things we did.

315
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:42,430
所有的死亡  日复一日
All that death, day after day after day...

316
00:36:43,980 --> 00:36:47,580
不久以后  我和你有了同样的想法
After a while, I started to feel like you.

317
00:36:49,290 --> 00:36:53,770
我在想  上帝哪去了
Wondering -- Wondering where God was.

318
00:36:55,160 --> 00:36:56,950
直到他再次现身
Until He showed His face again.

319
00:36:57,320 --> 00:37:00,900
政客们  还有最后一场仗要打
See, politicians -- they had one last war to get behind.

320
00:37:00,900 --> 00:37:04,430
这一次  敌人是我们
This time, coming for us.

321
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:10,690
炸弹如暴雨般落下
The bombs came thick and fast.

322
00:37:11,830 --> 00:37:13,150
一直没有停
It did not stop.

323
00:37:14,910 --> 00:37:16,980
我们和一些战友走散了
We lost some of our own,

324
00:37:18,040 --> 00:37:20,090
不得不穿越大火去救他们
had to run through the fire to save them.

325
00:37:22,650 --> 00:37:24,940
我们在城镇边缘找到了一座小教堂
Found this little church at the edge of town,

326
00:37:24,950 --> 00:37:26,660
我们躲在那里  看着一切
and we holed up there as everything --

327
00:37:26,660 --> 00:37:31,940
我是说所有的一切  在身边燃烧
and I mean everything -- burned around us.

328
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:37,030
等火终于熄灭了
When the fires finally died down,

329
00:37:37,030 --> 00:37:38,600
我看向我的部下
I looked at my people...

330
00:37:41,170 --> 00:37:43,090
我简直不敢相信
I could not believe it.

331
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:47,560
没留一滴血
Not a trace of blood.

332
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:50,460
没有烧伤
No burn marks.

333
00:37:51,670 --> 00:37:54,550
连擦伤都没有
Not even a scratch.

334
00:37:56,240 --> 00:37:57,770
那时我就知道了
And that's when I knew.

335
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:05,270
我们是天选之人
We were the Chosen Ones.

336
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:09,650
这些人
These men --

337
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:15,780
火焰伤不了这些人的身躯
These men upon whose bodies the fire had no power.

338
00:38:21,540 --> 00:38:23,230
上帝今晚选中了你
God chose you tonight.

339
00:38:24,620 --> 00:38:30,230
你毫发无伤  活着逃出了火场
I mean, you -- you came out of that fire alive and whole.

340
00:38:31,470 --> 00:38:34,130
看看你  现在坐在这里
And look at you now, sitting right here.

341
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:35,870
你受伤了吗
Are you hurt?

342
00:38:37,620 --> 00:38:38,850
被烧到了吗
Any burns?

343
00:38:39,950 --> 00:38:41,110
有擦伤吗
A scratch?

344
00:38:44,550 --> 00:38:46,350
我以前经历过更糟的事
I've been through worse before.

345
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:58,450
你饿吗
Are. You. Hungry?

346
00:39:32,530 --> 00:39:33,500
你说得对
You were right.

347
00:39:33,570 --> 00:39:34,550
关于这家伙
About this one.

348
00:39:35,930 --> 00:39:36,880
我当然对了
Of course I was.

349
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:42,040
分他点  博西
Give him some, Bossie.

350
00:39:42,690 --> 00:39:43,790
别太贪
Don't be greedy.

351
00:39:45,290 --> 00:39:46,770
他现在是家人了
He's family now.

352
00:39:54,050 --> 00:39:56,380
你知道他做了什么吧
You know what he did, don't you?

353
00:39:56,940 --> 00:40:02,380
他背着死去的兄弟走了10英里
He walked 10 miles with his dead brother on his back.

354
00:40:03,080 --> 00:40:04,190
10英里
10 miles.

355
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:07,800
这需要多大的力量啊
The strength that took...

356
00:40:09,950 --> 00:40:12,360
你知道我们有多感激吗
You have any idea how grateful we are?

357
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:18,040
特纳会有一个体面的葬礼
Turner will have a proper burial.

358
00:40:18,040 --> 00:40:20,750
我只是做了我们都会做的事
Just did what any one of us would've done.

359
00:40:30,970 --> 00:40:32,000
还疼吗
These still hurt?

360
00:40:34,550 --> 00:40:35,630
需要什么吗
You need anything?

361
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:44,220
我只想问一个问题
I just have one question.

362
00:40:45,570 --> 00:40:46,730
好
S-Sure.

363
00:40:47,960 --> 00:40:49,720
有件事我一直很困惑
Something's been bothering me.

364
00:40:51,530 --> 00:40:52,630
你的伤口
Your wounds...

365
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:55,280
在背上
are on your back.

366
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:58,360
教皇  今天已经够辛苦了
Pope, it's been a rough day.

367
00:40:58,360 --> 00:41:00,960
我只是想弄清楚  肖
Just getting clarity, Shaw.

368
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:08,510
特纳被袭击时  你在哪里
Where were you when Turner was being attacked?

369
00:41:08,510 --> 00:41:10,610
我在现场  我给你说过了
I-I was right there, just like I told you.

370
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:13,710
面朝敌人吗
Facing the enemy?

371
00:41:14,870 --> 00:41:15,710
对
Yeah.

372
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,200
他受的苦够多了
He's been through enough.

373
00:41:28,450 --> 00:41:31,690
害怕了会跑是人的本能反应
Human nature is to run when you are scared.

374
00:41:32,680 --> 00:41:34,790
你懂的吧
You know what that's like, right?

375
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:43,480
直面恐惧需要非凡的勇气
It takes divine strength to face your fear head-on.

376
00:41:44,730 --> 00:41:47,240
为别人赌上一切
Risk everything for someone else.

377
00:41:48,510 --> 00:41:50,710
我们都看到了你所做的事
We all saw what you did.

378
00:41:51,120 --> 00:41:55,130
先把肖救出火场  你也感受到了吧
Getting Shaw out of the fire first, and you felt it, huh?

379
00:41:56,220 --> 00:42:00,710
