How far he would go just to keep you safe.

380
00:42:02,450 --> 00:42:06,970
今天  上帝用火洗礼了你
Today, God baptized you in that fire.

381
00:42:09,230 --> 00:42:11,440
让你成了我们的一员
Made you one of us.

382
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:15,360
不过
You see...

383
00:42:16,870 --> 00:42:20,290
我忘了告诉你一件事
there's one thing I forgot to tell you.

384
00:42:20,570 --> 00:42:22,970
永远不要背弃你的兄弟
Never turn your back on your brother.

385
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:32,280
上帝不只用火来洗礼
God doesn't only use fire as His baptism.

386
00:42:37,300 --> 00:42:38,860
他也用火来表达愤怒
It's also His wrath.

387
00:43:05,470 --> 00:43:07,780
我们是天选之人
We are the Chosen Ones!

388
00:43:09,410 --> 00:43:12,640
我们奔向战场
We run into the battle.

389
00:43:13,050 --> 00:43:15,610
我们奔入火场
We run into the fire.

390
00:43:20,050 --> 00:43:21,700
永远如此
Always.


